在[[電磁波譜|電磁波譜]]中，'''紅邊'''是[[植被|植被]]的反射率在[[红外线#不同領域的紅外線|近紅外線]]波段接近與紅光交界處快速變化的區域。植被中的[[叶绿素|叶绿素]]會吸收大部分的可見光，但對於波長700 [[奈米|nm]]以上電磁波是幾乎透明的。因此，植被的細胞結構是反射電磁波的主要部分，這是因為每個[[細胞|細胞]]的反射機制類似小型的{{link-en|角反射器|Corner reflector}}。因此植物在680到730 nm電磁波反射率可從5%快速變化為50%<ref>{{cite journal | last1=Horler | first1=D. N. H. | last2=Dockray | first2=M. | last3=Barber | first3=M. | year=1983 | title=The red edge of plant leaf reflectance | journal=International Journal of Remote Sensing | pmid= | volume=4 | issue=2 | pages=273-288 | doi=10.1080/01431168308948546 | bibcode= |arxiv =  }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1=Fiella | first1=I. | last2=Penuelas | first2=J. | year=1994 | title=The red edge position and shape as indicators of plant chlorophyll content, biomass and hydric status | journal=International Journal of Remote Sensing | pmid= | volume=15 | issue=7 | pages=1459-1470 | doi=10.1080/01431169408954177 | bibcode= |arxiv =  }}</ref>。

這個現象可以用來解釋在{{link-en|紅外線攝影|Infrared photography}}中植物葉片相當明亮的原因，並且被應用在植物生長狀態的植被指數上（例如[[常態化差值植生指標|常態化差值植生指標]]，NDVI）。在[[遥感|遥感]]中紅邊波段可用來監測植物活性，並且被建議作為偵測遙遠行星中是否有生物之用<ref>{{cite journal | last1=Seager | first1=S. | last2=Turner | first2=E.L. | last3=Schafer | first3=J. | last4=Ford | first4=E.B. | year=2005 | title=Vegetation's Red Edge: A Possible Spectroscopic Biosignature of Extraterrestrial Plants | journal=Astrobiology | pmid=15941381 | volume=5 | issue=3 | pages=372–390 | doi=10.1089/ast.2005.5.372 | bibcode=2005AsBio...5..372S |arxiv = astro-ph/0503302 }}</ref>。

目前地球資源衛星中有德國的 {{link-en|RapidEye|RapidEye}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blackbridge.com/rapideye/upload/Red_Edge_White_Paper.pdf |title=The RapidEye Red Edge Band |access-date=2014-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140329094944/http://blackbridge.com/rapideye/upload/Red_Edge_White_Paper.pdf |archive-date=2014-03-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 和美國的 {{link-en|WorldView-2|WorldView-2}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.satimagingcorp.com/media/pdf/WorldView-2_8-Band_Applications_Whitepaper.pdf |title=The Benefits of the 8 Spectral Bands of WorldView-2 |access-date=2014-03-29 |archive-date=2012-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012151754/http://www.satimagingcorp.com/media/pdf/WorldView-2_8-Band_Applications_Whitepaper.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>、{{link-en|WorldView-3|WorldView-3}}<ref name="eoPortal_WV3">{{cite web |url=https://directory.eoportal.org/web/eoportal/satellite-missions/v-w-x-y-z/worldview-3 |title=WorldView-3 (WV-3) |work=eoPortal |publisher=European Space Agency |accessdate=2014-08-13 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119121835/https://directory.eoportal.org/web/eoportal/satellite-missions/v-w-x-y-z/worldview-3 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 、[[歐洲太空總署|歐洲太空總署]]的[[哨兵2号|哨兵2号]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Observing_the_Earth/Copernicus/Sentinel-2/Instrument |title=Instrument / Sentinel-2 / Copernicus / Observing the Earth / Our - ESA |access-date=2016-10-20 |archive-date=2019-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191011051908/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Observing_the_Earth/Copernicus/Sentinel-2/Instrument |dead-url=no }}</ref>有紅邊波段。

